ATTACHMENT A
Rate Schedule FERC No. 1 Ingenco Wholesale Power, LLC Reactive Power Compensation
INGENCO WHOLESALE POWER, LLC
RATE SCHEDULE FERC NO. 1
Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service
Ingenco Wholesale Power, LLC ("Ingenco") provides Reactive Supply and Voltage Control from Generation Sources Service ("Reactive Supply Service") from 15 generating facilities interconnected to transmission facilities owned by Virginia Electric and Power Company d/b/a Dominion Virginia Power, Appalachian Power Company, PPL Electric Utilities Corporation, West Penn Power Company and Delmarva Power and Light Company and under the operational control of the PJM Interconnection, L.L.C. ("Ingenco Facilities").
This Rate Schedule FERC No. 1 sets forth Ingenco's revenue requirement for Reactive Supply Service from the Ingenco Facilities. This Rate Schedule shall be effective upon the date authorized by the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission.
Ingenco's monthly fixed revenue requirement consists of the charge for the Fixed Capability Component. Payment to Ingenco shall be subject to Schedule 2 of PJM's Open Access Transmission Tariff.
Virginia Electric and Power Company d/b/a Dominion Virginia Power Zone
The Annual Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $888,913.24. The Monthly Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $74,076.10.
Appalachian Power Company Zone
The Annual Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $39,025.58. The Monthly Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $3,252.13.
PPL Electric Utilities Corporation Zone
The Annual Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $34,670.56?. The Monthly Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $?2,899.21?.
West Penn Power Company Zone
The Annual Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $83,627.20. The Monthly Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $6,968.93.
Delmarva Power and Light Company Zone
The Annual Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $?45,545.77?. The Monthly Reactive Service Revenue Requirement is: $?3,795.48?.
